$ gcc -shared
@ -shared

Instruct the → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/linker to create a *shared object*.

Although `-shared` is an option for the → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/linker[linker], it does not need to be passed with
→ development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/options/Wl[`-Wl`].

sa:

  → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/create-libraries

  → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/options/f/pic[`-fpic`, `-fPIC`]

  → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/options
